729108f-a.title: Richmond: Manor Road - Sturges Street
729108f-a.text:
466 Manor Road, west side, at the head of Sturges Street. This
house belonged to A. W. Goodell (1874 map), G. Brehme (1898 map),
Agatha Brehme (1907), and Joseph RoVengo (1917 map). The Brehmes
oalled the mansion the ''Spruce Grove''.
May 4, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
